'''Gonorrhea''' is a [[disease]]. It is transmitted by having [[sexual intercourse|sex]]. It is among the most widespread [[sexually transmitted disease]]s, but can be cured using [[antibiotic]]s. 

== Cleanup ==
It is caused by a [[bacteria|bacterium]], ''Neisseria gonorrheae''. Since it is caused by a bacterium, it can be treated with [[antibiotics]]. The use of [[latex]] [[condom]]s when having sex can prevent it from spreading.


